All Classes

Class Summary
Class Description
Actor
This is an abstract class of Actor where other game elements like Frogger, Turtle, Log...
BackgroundImage
This is a BackgroundImage class where it takes a image and output it with correct size to fit the window.
Button
This is the Button class where it handles the click animation of the button and how the button looks like.
Digit
This is the Digit class where it will show the score of the game.
End
This is the End class to create End Portals for the game.
Frogger
This is the Frogger class, the main character of the game.
Log
This is the Log class where it will create a Log for Frogger to step over in the game.
Main
This is the Main class of the game.
MusicButton
This is the MusicButton class where this button can mute/unmute the game background music.
MyStage
This is the MyStage class where it inherits from abstract class World.
Obstacle
This is the Log class where it will create obstacle to prevent Frogger going towards End Portal smoothly.
Turtle
This is the Turtle class where it will create turtles for Frogger to step over in the game.
WetTurtle
This is the Wet Turtle class where it will create wet turtles for Frogger to step over in the game.
World
This is abstract class World where it handles mostly animation and generation of game assets.
